## Performance

### Database Optimization
- Use database indexes on frequently queried columns
- Implement pagination for list endpoints
- Use eager loading to avoid N+1 queries: `db.session.query(Model).options(joinedload(Model.relation))`

### Caching
- Consider Flask-Caching for expensive operations
- Cache Databricks metadata that changes infrequently